INSERT INTO `diarys_diary` VALUES (1,'北京雪乡游玩功略','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">去年冬天，我和朋友一起去东北玩了6天，我们的时间比较充裕，所以把哈尔滨/雪乡/亚布力/冰雪大世界/威虎寨等景区都玩遍了，不留一点遗憾。惊喜的是我们每人才花费1000多元，真是太惊喜太值了！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>我们全程住的五星级酒店，免费赠送的冰雪大世界门票，亚布力滑雪场畅玩不限制滑雪时间，这种体验是一生难忘的，今年我真的好想再去一次！</strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">一直梦想着去千里冰封、万里雪飘的冰雪之都东北，给朋友们看了宛如童话般的东北雪景后，他们也挺想去看看。东北景点太分散，坐车安排路线太麻烦，酒店的预订、景点门票一大堆事情，没有当地导游带你玩给你讲解景点，根本玩不到精华。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 102, 255);\"><strong>费用明细：</strong></span><br/><span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">1、往返东北的机票是我们自己花钱预定的。<br/>2、全程的住宿、餐饮、导游、门票、交通等都包含在费用里，到东北后只要开心游玩景点就OK了！<br/>3、专享当地导游细致讲解，当地陪同游览（<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>很细心、服务周到）<br/>4、舌尖美味：东北特色美食，特色杀猪菜、满族乌拉火锅、关东八大碗。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">个人觉得费用很划算，超值了。并且玩的很自由很开心，再次感谢全程给我们安排的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>.</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">出发之前，在网上也联系了几家，看<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>导游评价很高，最终选择<span class=\"kefuSex\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">她</span>，<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>导游确实很热情，我加了<span class=\"kefuSex\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">她</span>的微信后，聊了很多，<span class=\"kefuSex\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">她</span>解答了我对此次东北旅行的众多疑问，我们聊了两天，人蛮实在，<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>是导游，闲暇时在网络上结识一些喜欢旅游的朋友。<span class=\"kefuSex\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">她</span>说就是想把这些共同想去东北的朋友凑成结伴同行，省时省钱省心省事，玩得开心还多交了朋友。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最终，我们和<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>确定了第一天抵达哈尔滨，中间游玩亚布力、雪乡、威虎寨，然后返回哈尔滨，游玩中央大街+圣·索菲亚教堂+冰雪大世界，最后从哈尔滨返程的旅游行程。我们给<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>提供了我们的身份信息，每人预付了200元的定金叫<span class=\"kefuSex\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">她</span>提前预约好酒店和门票，因为东北的酒店和门票、车票都要提前预定才能安排。<br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">我们自己坐飞机去的哈尔滨，<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>早就安排了工作人员在机场出口接我们，接到我们后就送我们到了住宿的酒店，签订正规旅游合同后，我们付了剩下的钱。接下来就开始我们期待的东北之旅了。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>第一天：抵达哈尔滨。</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">抵达哈尔滨当天，<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>安排我们入住了市区酒店，我们下午在哈尔滨市区逛了逛，晚上在酒店附近的冷饮店吃了最正宗的哈尔滨特色美食——<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【马迭尔冰棍】</span>。说实在的，坐那么久的飞机又逛街有点累。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>第二天：游览亚布力滑雪场。</strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">早餐后，<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>导游安排我们乘车前往亚洲最大的国际滑雪中心——<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【亚布力滑雪度假区】</span>。<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>导游就像行走的东北百科全书，感觉<span class=\"kefuSex\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">她</span>既是导游，也像我们的朋友，幽默、风趣的语言让我们感受到了东北独有的文化。上午抵达亚布力后，我们首先乘坐堪称中国最长雪道的<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【高山索道】</span>至亚布力最高峰，沿途欣赏林海雪原，参观著名影视作品“林海雪原”的拍摄地，偃松、石海、树挂等胜景，登顶<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【大锅盔山】</span>，观亚布力景区全景。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">然后，<span class=\"kefuName\" style=\"font-weight: inherit;\">秀秀</span>带着我们乘坐<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【世界第一滑道】</span>滑行下山，这条滑道宛如一条长龙，沿山坡向下延伸，全长2680米，有48个弯道，在这条隧道里，可以体会超越时空，势不可挡的冲击感、征服感和成就感。惊险刺激，让人意犹未尽！</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">下午，我们来到<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【亚布力国际滑雪中心】</span>，亲自体验惊险而刺激的贵族运动——滑雪，我们还体验了<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【山地车雪中越野】</span>、<span style=\"color: rgb(52, 152, 219);\">【雪上飞碟】</span>等项目，说实话，我们在这里可以玩一整天不带重样的。<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">（虽然我们不会滑雪，不知道摔了多少跤，可是玩的非常开心，绝对是一次不错的体验！）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p><br/></p>','diary/2022/01/note_1.jpg',12,0,3,1,1,'2022-01-01 11:19:26.814847',1),(2,'北京三日游玩攻略','<p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\">游玩攻略</span></p><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>上午</p><p>早晨前往天安门广场，体会这座世界最大广场的庄严气魄。（要是想看升旗的话一定要赶早，因为升旗时间与日出时间一致，所以要事先查好信息，至少提前一小时左右到场）看过英雄纪念碑、毛主席纪念堂、人民大会堂等建筑后，可以去前门一带溜溜逛逛，感受下老北京购物街的风情，顺便在这吃午饭。</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3498.html\" data-time=\"1.5小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">天安门广场</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(1.5小时)</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"transport \" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 16px 0px 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(239, 239, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 12px; position: relative; vertical-align: top;\">步行15分钟<em class=\"i-arrow\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 10px; height: 7px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/10220.html\" data-time=\"1.5小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">前门大街</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(1.5小时)</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"transport \" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 16px 0px 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(239, 239, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 12px; position: relative; vertical-align: top;\">步行5分钟<em class=\"i-arrow\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 10px; height: 7px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" data-time=\"1小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">北京全聚德(前门店)</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(1小时)</span></span></p></li><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3498.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/5D/C6/wKgBs1bwDfCAIkuCAAr8itczKQo18.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/5D/C6/wKgBs1bwDfCAIkuCAAr8itczKQo18.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3498.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">天安门广场</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">天安门广场</h3></li><li><p>北京旅游的代表性景点之一，可以在这观看升降旗，广场上还有人民英雄纪念碑、毛主席纪念堂</p></li></ul><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/10220.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D0/81/wKgBEFt5azCAEklYABXzznZs6p441.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/D0/81/wKgBEFt5azCAEklYABXzznZs6p441.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/10220.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">前门大街</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">前门大街</h3></li><li><p>北京最著名的老街之一，云集了不少上百年的老字号店铺，步行街上还有观光用的铛铛车。</p></li></ul><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/59/E7/wKgBEFrwfKGANi40AA-qYKEIMWQ58.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/59/E7/wKgBEFrwfKGANi40AA-qYKEIMWQ58.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">北京全聚德(前门店)</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">北京全聚德(前门店)</h3></li><li><p><br/></p></li></ul></ul><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>下午</p><p>用过午餐后，可以乘公交回到天安门城楼附近，开始下午的故宫之行。故宫景区比较大，游览点多，在参观之前最好做一些功课，或者跟着导游听讲解。从故宫北门出来便来到了景山公园，登上景山就可以看到故宫全景与360度无死角的北京全貌。如果还有体力，黄昏时可以去周边的胡同里随意逛逛，感受北京最真实的市井生活</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3474.html\" data-time=\"3小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">故宫</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(3小时)</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"transport \" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 16px 0px 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(239, 239, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 12px; position: relative; vertical-align: top;\">步行5分钟<em class=\"i-arrow\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 10px; height: 7px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3562.html\" data-time=\"1小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">景山公园</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(1小时)</span></span></p></li><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3474.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/D3/wKgBZ1t__3WAWS0WAA7im9BjWeg67.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/55/D3/wKgBZ1t__3WAWS0WAA7im9BjWeg67.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3474.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">故宫</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">故宫</h3></li><li><p>中国乃至世界上保存最完整，规模最大的木质结构古建筑群，在这里感受中华文明的历代传承。</p></li></ul><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3562.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/A8/2A/wKgBEFt4rEGAI5dYAENQOfwdpe829.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/A8/2A/wKgBEFt4rEGAI5dYAENQOfwdpe829.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3562.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">景山公园</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">景山公园</h3></li><li><p>位于北京中轴线，曾是全城的制高点，可俯瞰故宫全景</p></li></ul></ul><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-traffic\" style=\"float: left; margin: 3px 10px 0px 0px; width: 16px; height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -50px -120px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>交通攻略</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">作为首都，北京的城市交通非常发达。地铁和公交是游客最常用的出行手段。到北京后，强烈建议在地铁站里办一张【市政交通一卡通】，地铁、公交与部分城市快轨都能够刷卡使用。</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">今日交通主要靠步行完成。在前门-大栅栏附近游览完，如果想回到天安门城楼附近去故宫游玩，可以在大栅栏公交站坐2/59/120路到天安门东站下车。</p><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-food\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 10px 0px 0px; width: 16px; height: 16px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -25px -120px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>餐饮攻略</span></p><p>北京数百年来都是各民族混居的国际大都会，故而这里的各路小吃也自成一家、咸甜丰富。北京菜虽没有列入八大菜系，但北京美食的名声早已流传在外，鲜香适口是北京菜的普遍特征。<br/><br/>前门大街汇聚了很多像全聚德、东来顺这样的老字号和其他北京美食的总店，各家餐厅总是人满为患。旁边的大栅栏胡同聚集了很多特色小吃，想吃爆肚、卤煮等美食的话，来这儿逛逛准没错。</p><ul class=\"food-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>前门-大栅栏周边美食</p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/59/E7/wKgBEFrwfKGANi40AA-qYKEIMWQ58.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/59/E7/wKgBEFrwfKGANi40AA-qYKEIMWQ58.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(244, 124, 104); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">烤鸭</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">北京全聚德(前门店)</a></h3><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3759.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">北京全聚德的旗舰店，口味最地道。</a></p><p></p></li><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">北京全聚德(前门店)</h3></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>位置：前门公交站向南200米<br/>价格：人均150元</p></li></ul><li><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6947012.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6947012.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/C1/BB/wKgED1w7UluAP_h6AAvpDf5N9fo32.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/C1/BB/wKgED1w7UluAP_h6AAvpDf5N9fo32.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6947012.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(244, 124, 104); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">烤鸭</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6947012.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">四季民福烤鸭店(前门廊坊二条二店)</a></h3><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6947012.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">价格相对全聚德更实惠的烤鸭店，当地人更爱来。</a></p><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">四季民福烤鸭店(前门廊坊二条二店)</h3></li><li><p>位置：廊房二条东段<br/>价格：人均107元</p></li></ul><li><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15322008.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15322008.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/97/9E/wKgBs1e7_imAYXx_AASiXtzjdq045.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/97/9E/wKgBs1e7_imAYXx_AASiXtzjdq045.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15322008.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(244, 124, 104); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">北京菜</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15322008.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">前门故事餐厅</a></h3><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15322008.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">走亲民路线的北京菜餐厅，店内装潢与服务人员都是一派民国范儿。</a></p><p></p></li><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">前门故事餐厅</h3></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>位置：杨梅竹斜街与煤市街交叉口<br/>价格：人均50元</p></li></ul><li><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/842308.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/842308.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s7/M00/25/2F/wKgB6lQ2UIOAL6OiAA0xL6AjPtU41.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s7/M00/25/2F/wKgB6lQ2UIOAL6OiAA0xL6AjPtU41.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/842308.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(244, 124, 104); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">创意菜</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/842308.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">院落创意菜(地安门店)</a></h3><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/842308.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">坐落在四合院里的私房菜馆，环境雅致、菜品出彩。</a></p><p></p></li><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">院落创意菜(地安门店)</h3></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>位置：西福寿里与东福寿里交叉口处<br/>价格：人均70元</p></li></ul></ul><p><span class=\"btn-slide btn-next bright\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 116px; width: 32px; height: 32px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -35px -170px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; z-index: 5; cursor: pointer; right: 20px;\"></span></p><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-hotel\" style=\"float: left; margin: 6px 10px 0px 0px; width: 19px; height: 12px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -40px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>住宿攻略</span></p><p>天安门-故宫-前门-王府井一带是北京的中心区域，各种档次的酒店数量都不少。北京的很多热门景点也位于上述区域内，可以很方便的到达。此外，地铁1号、2号线经过该区域，极大方便游人出行。</p><ul class=\"figure-box list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><a data-t=\"hotel\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/area_45.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/77/5B/wKgBZ1mBnIGAGD4gAACw8Rq2ZmE806.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21540x360r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21540x360%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></a></p><p><a data-t=\"hotel\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/area_45.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><span class=\"tag tag-blue\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(10, 137, 228); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">住宿</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"hotel\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/area_45.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">天安门周边</a></h3><p></p></li><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">天安门周边</h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 157, 0); padding: 0px 3px;\">30%</span>&nbsp;会住在天安门周边街区</p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>有<span class=\"num\">189</span>家酒店。这里是北京的最中心，拥有北京的标志——天安门，故宫。 住在这附近，步行即可达天安门广场，可...</p></li></ul></ul><p><span class=\"day-num\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -62px; width: 45px; height: 45px; text-align: center; line-height: 44px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 50%; background-color: rgb(116, 121, 130);\">D2</span><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-scenic\" style=\"float: left; margin: 4px 10px 0px 0px; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -25px -40px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>游玩攻略</span></p><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>上午</p><p>今天上午前往天坛参观，该景区分东南西北四个出入口，建议从南门进、北门出，这样能够按照圜丘坛、回音壁、祈年殿的顺序参观，以获得最佳的游览体验。</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3503.html\" data-time=\"2.5小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">天坛</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(2.5小时)</span></span></p></li><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3503.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/E4/97/wKgED1v9AMWAD1W8AArZGbRQIv855.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/E4/97/wKgED1v9AMWAD1W8AArZGbRQIv855.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3503.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">天坛</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">天坛</h3></li><li><p>明清两代皇帝祭祀天地之神和祈祷五谷丰收的地方</p></li></ul></ul><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>下午</p><p>下午前往雍和宫一带游览。作为北京最大的藏传佛教寺院与雍正皇帝的前府邸，雍和宫的人气与贵气都是其他佛寺难以匹敌的，非常值得一看。参观完了雍和宫，可以去街对面的孔庙国子监游览，强烈建议跟着内部导游进行参观，不然很多的细节只凭自己的话无法全面了解。</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3516.html\" data-time=\"2小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">雍和宫</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(2小时)</span></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"transport \" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 16px 0px 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(239, 239, 238); line-height: 24px; font-size: 12px; position: relative; vertical-align: top;\">步行8分钟<em class=\"i-arrow\" style=\"position: absolute; right: 0px; bottom: 0px; width: 10px; height: 7px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px 0px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em></span>&nbsp;<span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3517.html\" data-time=\"1.5小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">孔庙和国子监博物馆</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(1.5小时)</span></span></p></li><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3516.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/44/9C/wKgBEFtGKyaAGcuvAF8nHEhBSnM69.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/44/9C/wKgBEFtGKyaAGcuvAF8nHEhBSnM69.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3516.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">雍和宫</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">雍和宫</h3></li><li><p>北京保存最完好的喇嘛教黄教寺院</p></li></ul><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3517.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/20/77/wKgED1xJL96AbHS4ABALCUudSII63.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s12/M00/20/77/wKgED1xJL96AbHS4ABALCUudSII63.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3517.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">孔庙和国子监博物馆</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">孔庙和国子监博物馆</h3></li><li><p>建筑古色古香，人文气息极其浓厚。</p></li></ul></ul><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>晚上</p><p>逛完了景点，晚上可以来到簋街附近吃大餐。这里云集着全国各地的美味，以麻辣口味为主，各家都有自家的招牌菜。当你在深夜游玩时，热闹的簋街灯火辉煌，一定会让你感受到北京的另一大魅力。</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3783.html\" data-time=\"2小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">簋街</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(2小时)</span></span></p></li><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3783.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/43/FD/wKgBZ1jtlR6AOZRkAARZyXSD9ts96.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/43/FD/wKgBZ1jtlR6AOZRkAARZyXSD9ts96.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3783.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">簋街</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">簋街</h3></li><li><p>不到1公里长的街上，一连串的餐馆饭庄，囊括了川、鲁、粤、湘的火锅、烧烤等各种风味美食</p></li></ul></ul><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-traffic\" style=\"float: left; margin: 3px 10px 0px 0px; width: 16px; height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -50px -120px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>交通攻略</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">今日行程交通主要依靠地铁完成。去天坛游玩的话，地铁5号线在天坛东门站A2口出站即可。结束天坛的行程后，可以继续坐地铁5号线至雍和宫站，C口出站即到景点。该日的其他行程步行即可完成。</p><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-food\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 10px 0px 0px; width: 16px; height: 16px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -25px -120px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>餐饮攻略</span></p><p>作为老北京的地标性建筑之一，天坛周围的各种美食也更是藏龙卧虎。从涮肉到各类特色小吃，讲求的是份高性价比的平民气质。<br/><br/>簋街则是京城内24小时狂欢的口腹之地。不到1公里长的街上，一连串的餐馆饭庄，囊括了川、鲁、粤、湘的火锅、烧烤等各种风味美食，属麻辣小龙虾、馋嘴蛙和烤鱼最为出名。簋街大红灯笼高高挂，已经成了北京最流行美食的风向标。</p><ul class=\"food-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>天坛</p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6123238.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6123238.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/AC/AD/wKgBEFqX7l2ADOpmABIlJcbA1yM92.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x1