; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6946871.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(244, 124, 104); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">清真菜</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6946871.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">阿兰菜馆</a></h3><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/6946871.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">据说是很多明星大腕经常光顾的餐馆，讲求地道的民族风。</a></p><p></p></li><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">阿兰菜馆</h3></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>位置：永定门东街与天坛东路交叉口<br/>价格：人均70元</p></li></ul><li><p><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>簋街</p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/847091.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/847091.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s14/M00/47/65/wKgE2l0a5y6ATMPcAAgWoE0346s960.jpg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%2127