x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3784.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><span class=\"tag\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(244, 124, 104); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">北京菜</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3784.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">花家怡园(四合院总店)</a></h3><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3784.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\">菜品选择比较多，尤其推荐京八件。店内也会有古筝、二胡等表演。</a></p><p></p></li><li><p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">花家怡园(四合院总店)</span><br/></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>位置：北新桥地铁站向东200米<br/>价格：人均150元</p></li></ul><li><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15325182.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15325182.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"><img width=\"270\" height=\"180\" class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/A7/08/wKgBs1e-ZnSAaKNRAAE-lKM87zY98.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s9/M00/A7/08/wKgBs1e-ZnSAaKNRAAE-lKM87zY98.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/15325182.html\" target