i><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">七寻八找鱼有余菜馆</h3></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>位置：北新桥地铁站向北250米<br/>价格：人均70元</p></li></ul></ul><p><span class=\"btn-slide btn-next bright\" style=\"position: absolute; top: 116px; width: 32px; height: 32px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -35px -170px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; z-index: 5; cursor: pointer; right: 20px;\"></span></p><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-hotel\" style=\"float: left; margin: 6px 10px 0px 0px; width: 19px; height: 12px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -40px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>住宿攻略</span></p><p>天安门-故宫-前门-王府井一带是北京的中心区域，各种档次的酒店数量都不少。北京的很多热门景点也位于上述区域内，可以很方便的到达。此外，地铁1号、2号线经过该区域，极大方便游人出行。</p><ul class=\"figure-box list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><a data-t=\"hotel\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/area_45.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s10/M00/77/5B/wKgBZ1mBnIGAGD4gAACw8Rq2ZmE806.png?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21540x360r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21540x360%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle;\"/></a></p><p><a data-t=\"hotel\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/area_45.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><span class=\"tag tag-blue\" style=\"float: right; padding: 0px 10px; text-align: center; line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(10, 137, 228); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 5px;\">住宿</span></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"hotel\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/hotel/area_45.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">天安门周边</a></h3><p></p></li><li><p><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">天安门周边</h3><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 157, 0); padding: 0px 3px;\">30%</span>&nbsp;会住在天安门周边街区</p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><p>有<span class=\"num\">189</span>家酒店。这里是北京的最中心，拥有北京的标志——天安门，故宫。 住在这附近，步行即可达天安门广场，可...</p></li></ul></ul><p><span class=\"day-num\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -62px; width: 45px; height: 45px; text-align: center; line-height: 44px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 50%; background-color: rgb(116, 121, 130);\">D3</span><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-scenic\" style=\"float: left; margin: 4px 10px 0px 0px; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -25px -40px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>游玩攻略</span></p><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>上午</p><p>上午前往“中国第一大贪官”和珅的府邸——恭王府游览，这座府邸的建筑布局从一些角度来说甚至比故宫的规格还要高。建议跟着导游讲解细细游览，否则会错过很多有趣的故事与细节。</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em><a class=\"p-link\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3506.html\" data-time=\"2.5小时\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block;\">恭王府</a><span class=\"time\" style=\"margin-left: 8px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-size: 12px;\">(2.5小时)</span></span></p></li><li><p><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3506.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\"><img class=\"lazy\" data-original=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CC/A0/wKgBEFqqyYGAI7PbAAvIIp4Q8qQ28.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" height=\"180\" width=\"270\" src=\"http://t1-q.mafengwo.net/s11/M00/CC/A0/wKgBEFqqyYGAI7PbAAvIIp4Q8qQ28.jpeg?imageMogr2%2Fthumbnail%2F%21270x180r%2Fgravity%2FCenter%2Fcrop%2F%21270x180%2Fquality%2F100\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; display: inline;\"/></a></p><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; font-weight: normal; line-height: 36px;\"><a data-t=\"poi\" class=\"figure\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3506.html\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer; float: left; margin-right: 15px; width: 270px; height: 180px; display: block; position: relative; overflow: hidden;\">恭王府</a></h3><p></p></li><ul class=\"middle list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: circle;\"><li><h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 20px; line-height: 24px; font-weight: normal;\">恭王府</h3></li><li><p>中国现存王府中保存最完整的清代王府</p></li></ul></ul><p><em class=\"i-mark\" style=\"float: left; margin: 0px 0px 0px -50px; width: 24px; height: 24px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: 0px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>下午</p><p>吃过午饭后便可到什刹海游玩，这里的小景点非常多，宋庆龄故居、郭沫若故居等都坐落于此。你也可以去烟袋斜街逛逛，感受深厚的市井风情和浓郁的老北京特色。往东北方向走，就能看见老北京的地标建筑——钟鼓楼。如果觉得不累，可以到拥挤的南锣鼓巷去瞧瞧，巷子两旁的胡同有着很多可以说道的历史。晚上可以到后海享受夜晚美景，有兴致的话不妨体验下这里的酒吧文化。</p><ul class=\"clearfix list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><span class=\"place\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 0px 20px 0px 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; b