tyle=\"float: left; margin: 3px 10px 0px 0px; width: 16px; height: 20px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -50px -120px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>交通攻略</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">恭王府位于什刹海西侧，地铁6号线北海北站下车后，向北步行300米即到。<br/>什刹海-钟鼓楼-南锣鼓巷一带依靠步行即可完成。该地区也可以乘坐人力三轮车游览，车夫会带着你逛胡同，顺带讲讲老北京故事。正规人力三轮车有服务价目表，清晰列出游览路线、游览时间以及每位游客的花费。</p><p><span class=\"tit\" style=\"display: inline-block; margin: 5px 20px 0px 0px; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); line-height: 24px; vertical-align: top;\"><em class=\"i-food\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 10px 0px 0px; width: 16px; height: 16px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -25px -120px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>餐饮攻略</span></p><p>什刹海/南锣鼓巷一带保留着老北京旧时的民风和历史，这里自然也少不了诸多老字号的身影，海边的一众酒吧也是如今这里的亮点。周边的胡同内则隐藏了诸多高质量的特色餐厅。在这儿要是找不到喜欢吃的东西，还真难。</p><ul class=\"food-list list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><li><p><em class=\"i-place\" style=\"float: left; margin: 5px 5px 0px 0px; width: 11px; height: 14px; background-image: url(&quot;/images/mdd/place/line-details-sprites7.png&quot;); background-position: -100px -145px; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; overflow: hidden;\"></em>什刹海/鼓楼/南锣鼓巷</p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3507.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); text-decoration-line: none; cursor: pointer;\"></a></p><p><a href=\"http://www.mafengwo.cn/poi/3507.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 157, 0); t