ine: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">隋文静</a></strong>和<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/cong-han/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">韩聪</a>（中国）</strong>是争夺金牌的热门人选。2018年冬奥会银牌得主和四届世界冠军<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/gabriella-papadakis/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">加布里埃拉·帕帕达吉斯</a>和<a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/guillaume-cizeron/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">纪尧姆·西泽龙</a>（法国）</strong>是冰舞金牌的有力竞争者。</p><p><br/> </p>','product/mainimg/2022/01/花样滑冰_42Zrd2S.jpg',NULL,'2022-01-02 15:38:00.000000'),(3,'短道速滑决赛门票',60,499,0,'北京冬奥会','ncp',1,0,'<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/media/shop/ueditor/短道速滑1_20220102155327_323.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"短道速滑1.jpg\"/>短道速滑是冬奥会三大滑冰赛事之一，与花样滑冰和速度滑冰齐名。但与速度滑冰不同的是，短道速滑比赛是参赛者之间的直接较量，而不是与时间赛跑。因此，短道速滑比赛策略、胆识、技巧和刺激并存。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">北京冬奥会短道速滑共设9个竞赛项目，包括首次亮相冬奥会的混合团体接力。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">观看<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://olympics.com/zh/beijing-2022/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">2022年北京冬奥会</a><a href=\"https://olympics.com/zh/sports/short-track-speed-skating/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">短道速滑</a></strong>前瞻，了解这项运动的历史、潜在的奖牌获得者以及比赛场地信息等。</p><p><br/></p>','product/mainimg/2022/01/短道速滑.png',NULL,'2022-01-02 15:50:00.000000'),(4,'自由式滑雪门票',50,397,0,'北京冬奥会','ncp',3,0,'<p><img src=\"/media/shop/ueditor/自由式滑雪1_20220102155835_662.jpg\" title=\"\" alt=\"自由式滑雪1.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\">1988年卡尔加里冬奥会</strong>上，自由式滑雪首次作为展示项目亮相奥运会赛场。之后于1992年正式纳入冬奥会比赛项目表当中。后来，自由式滑雪项目又增加了新项目：包括障碍追逐、U型场地技巧和坡面障碍技巧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2022年北京冬奥会自由式滑雪将展开13个项目的争夺，其中包括两个新项目——男子和女子<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\">自由式滑雪大跳台</strong>以及<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\">自由式滑雪空中技巧混合团体赛</strong>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在这里，您可以了解2022年<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://olympics.com/zh/beijing-2022/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">北京冬奥会</a><a href=\"https://olympics.com/zh/sports/freestyle-skiing/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">自由式滑雪</a></strong>项目的相关信息：包括这项运动的历史、值得关注的顶级选手以及场地信息等！</p><h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 60px; line-height: 70px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2022年北京冬奥会自由式滑雪顶级运动员</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当今自由式滑雪界两个最响亮的名字分别是<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/perrine-laffont/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">珀赖因·拉丰</a>（法国）</strong>和<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/mikael-kingsbury/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">米凯尔·金斯伯里</a>（加拿大）</strong>。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">金斯伯里是2018年平昌冬奥会男子雪上技巧冠军，是有史以来成就最高的雪上技巧大师。他手握多项纪录，他的男子雪上技巧世界杯总冠军数量、世界杯分站赛夺冠次数均为历史之最。此外，他也是自由式滑雪世锦赛历史上赢得奖牌最多的男子运动员（所有男子项目均包括在内）。此外，他还是雪上技巧和双雪上技巧卫冕世界冠军。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">拉丰也在平昌冬奥会赢得了女子雪上技巧赛事金牌。此外，她也是自由式滑雪赛季总冠军水晶金球奖杯（颁发给各单项和总成绩赛季积分榜最高排名者）得主，并赢得2021年世锦赛女子雪上技巧赛事金牌。</p><p><section class=\"story-content__embedded story-content__vod b2p-grid__2-10\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; grid-column: 2 / 10; overflow: hidden; outline: none; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica