m/images/image/private/t_16-9_1920/primary/dokfjek71i2flmins3zw&quot;,&quot;https://img.olympicchannel.com/images/image/private/t_16-9_3200/primary/dokfjek71i2flmins3zw&quot;,&quot;https://img.olympicchannel.com/images/image/private/t_16-9_1280/primary/dokfjek71i2flmins3zw&quot;,&quot;https://img.olympicchannel.com/images/image/private/t_16-9_1920/primary/dokfjek71i2flmins3zw&quot;,&quot;https://img.olympicchannel.com/images/image/private/t_16-9_760/primary/dokfjek71i2flmins3zw&quot;,&quot;https://img.olympicchannel.com/images/image/private/t_16-9_1280/primary/dokfjek71i2flmins3zw&quot;],&quot;datePublished&quot;:&quot;2021-03-16T10:06:50.000Z&quot;,&quot;dateModified&quot;:&quot;2021-11-25T17:54:10.081Z&quot;,&quot;author&quot;:{&quot;@type&quot;:&quot;Person&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;Will Imbo&quot;},&quot;publisher&quot;:{&quot;@type&quot;:&quot;Organization&quot;,&quot;name&quot;:&quot;International Olympic Committee&quot;,&quot;logo&quot;:{&quot;@type&quot;:&quot;ImageObject&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://olympics.com/images/static/oc_logo_60h-v2.png&quot;}}}}\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-top-navigation-by-user-activation\" src=\"https://olympics.com/zh/video/amp/syndicated/mikael-kingsbury-every-olympic-medal-race/?partnerdomain=olympicchannel.com#amp=1\" class=\"i-amphtml-fill-content\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: auto; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; vertical-align: baseline; display: block; height: 0px; max-height: 100%; max-width: 100%; min-height: 100%; min-width: 100%; width: 0px; outline: none; position: absolute; inset: 0px; overflow: hidden;\"></iframe><a href=\"https://olympics.com/zh/video/mikael-kingsbury-every-olympic-medal-race\" style=\"font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none;\">米凯尔·金斯伯利：奥运夺牌表现全回顾</a><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">U型场地技巧方面，2018年奥运会冠军</span><strong style=\"font-size: 20px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/cassie-sharpe/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">凯西·夏普</a></strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">（加拿大）在过去三年的X Games赛上均获得了超级U型场地技巧奖牌（2021年获得银牌，2020年和2019年获得铜牌），状态正佳。然而，她可能会面临来自谷爱凌（中国）的强大挑战。年仅17岁的谷爱凌在2021年世锦赛上赢得了U型场地技巧和坡面障碍技巧金牌。</span></amp-video-iframe></section></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">两届冬奥会金牌得主（2014年和2018年）<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/david-wise/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">大卫·怀斯</a></strong>（美国）是男子U型场地技巧项目的巨星之一。北京赛场上，他可能将面临同胞、两届世界冠军艾伦·布伦克以及2018年冬奥会铜牌得主、2021年世界冠军尼科·波蒂厄斯（新西兰）的挑战。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">坡面障碍技巧赛的争夺相当开放，将会亮相北京并引发广泛关注的选手包括世锦赛卫冕冠军、世界杯历史上夺得赛季总冠军次数最多的<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/andri-ragettli/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">安德里·拉吉特里</a></strong>（瑞士）<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\">、</strong>2019年世锦赛冠军<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/james-woods/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">詹姆斯·伍兹</a></strong>（德国）<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\">，</strong>以及冬奥会卫冕奥运冠军兼水晶球奖杯得主<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://www.olympicchannel.com/zh/athletes/detail/sarah-hoefflin/\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">萨拉·霍夫林</a></strong>（瑞士）。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; grid-column: 3 / 9; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, sans-serif, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; line-height: 32px; outline: none; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2017年和2021年障碍追逐世界冠军<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\">桑德拉·奈斯伦德</strong>（瑞典）是北京冬奥会女子障碍追逐赛的夺冠热门人选。世界冠军亚历克斯·费瓦（瑞士）和弗朗索瓦·普莱斯（法国）将在男子赛事上挑战奥运卫冕冠军<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none;\"><a href=\"https://olympics.com/zh/athletes/brady-leman\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; box-shadow: rgb(0, 0, 0) 0px 1px 0px 0px; display: inline-block;\">布雷迪·勒曼</a></strong>（加拿大）。</p><p><br/></p>','p